      "source": [
        "## 6. 🔎 Part 3: Design Decision 2 - The Retriever\n",
        "\n",
        "The Retriever finds the best chunks. We will build a two-stage process:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **Stage 1 (Fast):** FAISS quickly finds 12 candidate chunks.\n",
        "2. **Stage 2 (Precise):** A Cross-Encoder re-ranks those 12 to find the best 3.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Task 6.1: Set Retrieval Parameters\n",
        "\n",
        "* **TOP_K:** The final number of chunks to send to the LLM.\n",
        "* **USE_RERANK:** Whether to use the (slower but more accurate) cross-encoder."
      ]
    },
