      "source": [
        "**YOUR ANSWER:**\n",
        "\n",
        "My AAR system can improve Fleet or Force Modernization in several ways. One example would be to analyze thousands of AARs and pinpoint bottlenecks with regards to equipment failures. Perhaps there's a certain weapon system that is frequently cited for degrading in specific environments. Traditionally, this level of detail can be easily overlooked as routine maintenance, but in reality there could be underlying causes to the weapons failure. This directly affects the tactical level as solving these complex issues will enable our troops to deploy without restrictions. Another example application would be to analyze AARs regarding joint operations. Joint operations are complex in nature, but our AAR analysis system can read through all these documents and find flaws in the system. This can outline factual claims about potential limiting factors and enable commanders at the operational level to rethink how to carry out their joint operations."
